Great Potential, But Memory Fails the StoryGrok’s got the spark—wit, real-time X data, and a bold vibe I vibe with—but it’s stumbling hard on what matters most: memory. I’ve spent days weaving a saga with it, pouring in details, only for it to forget chunks or twist our shared history into something unrecognizable.
